column5: I,ll bet we seen 3 different class years today. Pinheads,2 inchers and 4-5 inchers.  Shinners
Get the nets out.  Slow the Seadoo down to trawl the bottom.  We need 2 grand to keep fishin.  Let's fish out the Atlantic.  Newfie.
Can we get an english translation?
If you get 1.3 perch for every minnow...... You would soon be sick of cleaning perch LOL.
Wow , that's an impressive baitfish population .
